  "Description": {
    "English": "A refined product, this is a powerful organic fertilizer in an easily distributed form.<br><br>Crafted from <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Nitrogen</span> and <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Condensed Carbon</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这是一种精炼产品，是强大的有机化肥，容易扩散。<br><br>由 <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氮</span>和<span class=\"name name-fuel\">凝聚碳</span>制作而成。",
    "TencentChinese": "这是一种精炼产品，是强大的有机化肥，容易扩散。<br><br>由 <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氮</span>和<span class=\"name name-fuel\">凝聚碳</span>制作而成。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "精製產品，形式方便配送的強力有機肥料。<br><br>可使用<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氮</span>與<span class=\"name name-fuel\">濃縮碳</span>製造。"
  },
