  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft from <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Nitrogen</span> and <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Condensed Carbon</span>. Learn the blueprint by raiding <span class=\"name name-technology\">planetary factories</span> or from the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Synthesis Lab</span> on the <span class=\"name name-special\">Space Anomaly</span>.<br>Harvest Nitrogen with an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Atmosphere Harvester</span> on <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Lush</span> and <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Toxic</span> worlds.<br>Refine Condensed Carbon from regular, plant-based <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Carbon</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "由<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氮</span>和<span class=\"name name-fuel\">浓缩碳</span>制作而成。通过突袭<span class=\"name name-technology\">行星工厂</span>或在<span class=\"name name-special\">太空异象</span>上的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">合成实验室</span>学习设计图。<br>在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">繁茂</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">毒性</span>世界使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">大气收集器</span>以收集氮。<br>使用星球上拥有的普通植物<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>精炼出浓缩碳。",
    "TencentChinese": "由<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氮</span>和<span class=\"name name-fuel\">浓缩碳</span>制作而成。通过突袭<span class=\"name name-technology\">行星工厂</span>学习设计图。<br>在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">茂盛</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">有毒</span>世界使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">大气采集器</span>以收集氮。<br>使用星球上拥有的普通<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>精炼出浓缩碳。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "以<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氮</span>及<span class=\"name name-fuel\">濃縮碳</span>製作。襲擊<span class=\"name name-technology\">星球工廠</span>或從<span class=\"name name-special\">太空異常</span>上的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">合成實驗室</span>來了解設計圖。<br>在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">蒼翠</span>及<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">劇毒</span>世界使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">大氣採集器</span>來採收氮。<br>將一般的植物<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>精製成濃縮碳。"
  },
